prompt:
You are a requirements rewriter.
Rewrite each requirement into clean natural language suitable for UML state diagram generation.

Return ONLY valid JSON with this schema:
{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "string",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall ..."
    }
  ]
}

Rules:
1. Keep exactly the same number of requirements and same order.
2. Do not add new meaning.
3. Each rewritten requirement must start with "The system shall".
4. Keep them concise and implementation-neutral.

Input JSON:
{
  "functional_requirements": [
    {
      "requirement": "The website should include major projects of the firm.",
      "evidence_quote": "The website of the firm should include the major projects of the firm,"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should have a brief on all available departments and collaborations.",
      "evidence_quote": "a brief on all the available departments and collaborations"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should display recent news with respect to the firm.",
      "evidence_quote": "recent news with respect to the firm,"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should include the firm's insights.",
      "evidence_quote": "the firm’s insights"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should have a history of the firm section.",
      "evidence_quote": "the history of the firm,"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should include a mail or chat feature.",
      "evidence_quote": "mail or chat feature"
    },
    {
      "requirement": "The website should have career opportunities with regard to the firm.",
      "evidence_quote": "career opportunities with regard to the firm (Figures 38.1–38.8)"
    }
  ]
}

llm_response:
Here is the rewritten JSON:

{
  "rewritten_requirements": [
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should include major projects of the firm.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall display a list of the firm's major projects on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should have a brief on all available departments and collaborations.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall provide a brief overview of all available departments and collaborations on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should display recent news with respect to the firm.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall display recent news related to the firm on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should include the firm's insights.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall provide access to the firm's insights on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should have a history of the firm section.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall include a section detailing the history of the firm on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should include a mail or chat feature.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall provide a mail or chat feature for user interaction on the website."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "The website should have career opportunities with regard to the firm.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall display information about career opportunities related to the firm on the website."
    }
  ]
}
